# Google Sign-In + Drive backup (OAuth 2.0)
# 0. Enable "Google Drive API" for the same project:
#    https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/library/drive.googleapis.com
# 1. https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# 2. Create OAuth client ID:
#    - Web application → EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_WEB_CLIENT_ID
#    - Android → package com.truongkieu.Serf + SHA-1 (keytool -list -v -keystore ~/.android/debug.keystore)
#    - iOS → bundle com.truongkieu.Serf
#    - Expo Go: dùng Web client ID → EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_EXPO_CLIENT_ID hoặc WEB_CLIENT_ID
# 3. Copy this file to .env and fill values, then rebuild: npx expo run:android

EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_WEB_CLIENT_ID=
EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_ANDROID_CLIENT_ID=
EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_IOS_CLIENT_ID=
EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_EXPO_CLIENT_ID=
